subject: Tennis
Sony Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams overcame a big deficit in her fourth-round match at the Sony Open in Key Biscayne, Fla., to beat Dominika Cibulkova, 2-6, 6-4, 6-2.
